[recv] {"type": "message_end", "message": {"role": "assistant", "content": [{"type": "thinking", "thinking": "**Examining Unicode Escapes**\n\nI'm considering how Java and Scala handle Unicode escapes. When there's a backslash followed by \"u\", it seems straightforward, but if there are two backslashes, I wonder if the second one can start a new sequence. To simplify matters, I think it might be best to avoid Unicode escapes completely or stick to single-line strings with an escaped backslash. In Scala, I see that the string \"\\u0041\" evaluates to \"A\".", "thinkingSignature": "{\"id\":\"rs_0e9a281b8a374085016a2ab32733c4819498d916cfbf6562f7\",\"type\":\"reasoning\",\"content\":[],\"encrypted_content\":\"gAAAAABqKrNGTWY8MbLT6NSWybsUu8eUaqS5QdqQhTH2TUqN9HK00aPuQLcXkG07UHnHT5DZtTUBk-7xCXsHZdP1M0h2PBppGky2eol10L-g2KWeObZpmCp--H8pdAwVwP1n6c4gx9LY69opBoW1RIr_wmfwU15mXsf_30N9Oeq1QvJeezuEwCYnj6zfp8SB346OTPpguMTO8fl2ZOEmB7rvsrghKisi7X6ULNJn9-8NYUV38uM1zNPOCTOXt_U8G7Oa3zVZcXkrRKJSWCx51ZaHy2tSmF1IJ0Au2673ZTTfh-wQQVKDzsJNfo9eAWho4D_7blB7zUff1Nl0y2KoqQ2Na_Dmlc81AvlxWJfY00bG-i1P0B6jNOrq8ZtAEca8bVCSI47TS7q9TB38qmObAIsvd7wT8PknswbaA-wqaerzdDDEOCq5ntNAHl8fhcOrAEnCxPpUaaQe1U-ZFVNEd_UjB0OjFyeKNIY1iZkaPKyh4IIkfZ5JGFC0hmNqhDYI4yikvIYRxmcPYfnHaage5nflS8UC1KdXrTsQCqYtWiIHd-ajnSH5sRpVIb42A8SebYjms1YY9wNGZJEC1Ji2W4auIZE18QmHNkgSIVci-CM7Q4adyOs6MPQsNj8vd0ay-Hs0knYkifkWxRlxvOhqasHP23mk3KC0Xp13h7ptMw5LKbyfvc58COC1c8voLd-xrF_kjRC31K265-hRN5_Ojydu53ge6fl6D3myC9S3_hyOKuFBAZkS7WvPq_IvffuLBvrkw_h08irfIAlxTUXf1lsPfTcdK1qC3hbGtLUXwQSzw9uHeFfQXgLdTFkomTkvQB3DGdTmMO_Ya3Ez_LE920M6xqS8tBZ5EGBltDF3oMdtcDZ8cK9cq5KknU08wnrUHIUH6ILcOMrTDT2Fon4QHx23aBWiUu7swEMEUkI_vH1CVxRp0MMINLZAfv6X9v1rBcA2IzBz4BPIk5Fzmag71FxculyNbAd4RPDxJZPliO7HQVoawjjpJgmtpRlOUlAvrEhHGMum7ZcyLQNWnHJ2Jv1JM2m5ESH2QlrBeyWFW4MCzQGE9PNgzb0N63OfDh2ew8IUtwJHAD1AVCUuDS4U4djgeTp2CpITEy5862jzY8He6MpiRKNHqi5fHKTUjNd2r-a8oqnHM_uZfe1MODPmMR6R7-lHX4MBWVGckV9oK1klxWO4ZB8k0FlzK0dV50s0dvnCOFQXw01O07QSC5MvqtVgEKstG-Qwhh6qAA_fyKIRNOfyVf8-pdmMv7Gr0IYlVVw8